    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"350992\">Rémy Degenne</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/prob.20and.20stats.20e.2Eg.2E.20in.20Lean4.20-.20linearity.20of.20expectation/near/562330301\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Note that you don't need independence for linearity of the expectation.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>thanks, yeah I removed that from my second code chunk. but also I'm trying to eventually do something more complicated that does require independence, which is why I got confused and added that in by mistake. so that original question/answer will not go to waste!</p>",
